        "Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera, United National Party MP Vajira Abeywardena, Samagi Jana Balavegaye's Thalatha Athukorala and Mr. Eran Wickramaratne have been newly appointed to the Parliamentary Affairs Committee."
